Context: The Behavioural Science Technician (C146) program is offered by George Brown College. For more information about the program content and potential career options, you can watch a previously recorded info session or contact Marlene Mcalpine at Marlene.Mcalpine@georgebrown.ca. Application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and other related information can be received by signing up on the website. The contact numbers for inquiries are 416-415-2000 (voice) and TTY: 1-877-515-5559. Additional information can be obtained by visiting the college's social media hub or sending an email to ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The contents of the website are subject to change without notice. It is important for students to verify George Brown College fee requirements.
